data.title: Office For Rent in Hyderabad: Pushpanjali Complex Main Rd Koti
data.meta_description: Hyderabad office space is now available in this business centre at Pushpanjali Complex,   13 Main Rd. Call us on +44 20 3998 2883 about serviced offices in Hyderabad and other prime business locations in India.
data.text:
This business centre located in Koti offers two cabins and 12 co-working desks for clients from any background. Services offered at this space are furnished offices, a conference room, high-speed internet and free water. If you are looking for a place to work and grow your business then this location will be perfect for you.

About this Location

This business centre is in the middle of the city which is suitable for all types of business, has easy access to bus stops, railway stations and atm's. This prime location also offers parking for those of you who drive to work. The space is well connected and ideal for those that wish to take public transport to work.
